    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>本演示中提供</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演圣骑士 圣骑士是战斗和防御的大师，是新玩家的最佳入门等级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索两个不同的区域，那里到处都是独特的敌人和 BOSS。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人，掠夺卡牌来升级你的卡组，并发现秘密力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 100 张卡牌是动态卡牌战的潜在战利品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.poster.avif?t=1757956413\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.webm?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.mp4?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双食》是一款适合在周末玩的短篇地牢爬行游戏，它以回合制战斗和取巧的方式进行。玩家将抵挡卡牌，用强大的日蚀卡牌扭转战局，并掠夺怪物来升级他们的卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演三个角色中的一个，探索神秘的地牢，躲避危险的陷阱，发掘强大的宝藏，探寻秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的取巧战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.poster.avif?t=1757956413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.webm?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.mp4?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗是通过 “取巧 ”来解决的！就像用纸牌击剑一样！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中，玩家和敌人都能控制获胜条件，因此每次遭遇战都会带来战略抉择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的组合能带来有趣的选择和动态的战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用功能强大的日蚀卡切换月亮和太阳，从而改变战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招架卡！提供高风险、高回报机会的战术选择。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级你的卡组，变得更强</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.poster.avif?t=1757956413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.webm?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145500/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.mp4?t=1757956413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人收集新卡，找到宝藏获得新力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得强大的能力和强化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级，专精等级，打造符合自己风格的游戏方式。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全面发布的计划</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游侠等级。由于缺乏强大的防御能力，“游侠 ”通过快速击败敌人来赢得战斗，并以精准取胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法师等级。在战斗中通过组合已打出的卡牌来创造独特的法术。为追求复杂性的玩家提供了高级选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面扩展的故事情节和全新的地牢探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多独特的遭遇、谜题、秘密和 BOSS。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新卡牌、特效和强力装备，扩展了卡组构建和进阶选项。</p></li></ul>",
